{"tid":666821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幻想成真？】又一黑科技！ 研究人員成功為蝸牛移植記憶","createTime":"2018-05-16T08:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T09:15:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"19eb69efc8ed5a764dfe9b9536a413c8e85f7b4d","tid":666821,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180516/large/1526432264_c4f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180516%2Flarge%2F1526432264_c4f9.jpg&h=8d0a0483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《神經科學學報》刊登文章，指有研究人員透過轉移遺傳訊息核糖核酸（RNA），成功把一隻蝸牛的記憶，移植到另一隻蝸牛身上，研究為尋找記憶的物理基礎提供新線索。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，科學家對一種名為Aplysia californica的海洋蝸牛的尾巴施加輕微電擊，令蝸牛出現反射反應，透過退縮來防禦和自衛。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員從受訓蝸牛的神經系統抽取RNA，再注入沒受訓練的蝸牛體內，結果後者出現類似的反應。<br />\n<br />\n有份撰寫研究報告的加州大學洛杉磯分校（UCLA）教授格蘭茲曼（David Glanzman）表示，研究成果「就像把記憶轉移了一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n傳統上，長期記憶被認為是存儲在大腦的突觸，即神經細胞之間的連接處。每個神經元都有幾千個突觸。<br />\n<br />\n惟格蘭茲曼表示：「如果記憶的確是儲存在突觸中，那麼我們的實驗就不可能成這個成果。」<br />\n<br />\n研究人員認為，實驗結果能為緩減腦退化症、或創傷後壓力症（PTSD）等疾病影響的研究帶來幫助。<br />\n<br />\n被問到實驗能否協助移植通過人生經歷而獲得的記憶時，格蘭茲曼教授稱未能確定，但亦表示樂觀，認為更深入理解儲存記憶的方法，會帶來更多探索記憶不同層面的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180516/58198001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58198001&d=tHclZjdFv0JrE21jMsQuEMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=689f1fae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180516%2F58198001&h=89b0cd5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180516/58198001</a>"},{"pid":"341afca913e44185db30c3dfbe1298ec62273879","tid":666821,"uid":170668,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"蝸牛好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545661ee23cf39882a62ca151d61bdf3026c3a1f","tid":666821,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"咁舊果隻既記憶會消失？"},{"pid":"91da32244e2b2833615087aac27b64b0190fec5a","tid":666821,"uid":44458,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"屌你你試下比野電鳩你縮唔縮？"},{"pid":"dd30ea2f0fb926f7c2b97a889ed52ef375dbba02","tid":666821,"uid":33481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91da32244e2b2833615087aac27b64b0190fec5a","tid":666821,"uid":44458,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"屌你你試下比野電鳩你縮唔縮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"會做對照架嘛"},{"pid":"13c0514cf80d41b06bc7228c3a3827d75e57d37a","tid":666821,"uid":19613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"刺客教條真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1d8e8c545e70a09cb04404af4daca2276424c6","tid":666821,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"記憶可以轉移=永生不死"},{"pid":"95b3cc2da16fb02a48a5c5fd80964d23000926dc","tid":666821,"uid":34461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:39:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，姐係原本電鳩佢，佢會無反應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14b7bde79f2afd24720b9c085aa5ed11d5e7d06","tid":666821,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:51:29.000Z","msg":"black mirror"},{"pid":"cbd48b3164dfec32d73ff68efdb03c7dcfea1e14","tid":666821,"uid":102240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"91da32244e2b2833615087aac27b64b0190fec5a","tid":666821,"uid":44458,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"屌你你試下比野電鳩你縮唔縮？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018